<i>verb</i>: 토라지다 [토라지다], 삐치다 [삐ː치다], 삐지다 [삐ː지다] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>verb</i><br>
<dt>토라지다 [토라지다]</dt><br>
<dd>pout; sulk</dd><br>
<dd>마음에 들지 않아 불만스러워 싹 돌아서다.</dd><br>
<dd>To turn away, as one does not approve or is not satisfied with something.</dd><br>
<dt>삐치다 [삐ː치다]</dt><br>
<dd>become sullen; sulk</dd><br>
<dd>화가 나거나 서운해서 마음이 뒤틀리다.</dd><br>
<dd>For one's mind to be twisted because one feels angry or hurt.</dd><br>
